---
const techStack = ['Astro 6', 'Tailwind 4', 'FastAPI', 'PostgreSQL + PostGIS', 'IBM Watsonx', 'OR-Tools', 'scikit-learn', 'Docker', 'Cloudflare Pages'];
---
<section id="arquitectura" class="mt-32 sm:mt-56">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl sm:text-center">
      <h2 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-eco-green">Tecnologia</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-pretty text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl sm:text-balance">Arquitectura de 4 capas</p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg/8 text-gray-600">Cada capa opera de forma independiente. Si una falla, las demas siguen funcionando.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Layer diagram -->
  <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-3xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl ring-1 ring-gray-900/10">
      <div class="bg-eco-green p-5 sm:p-6 text-white">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-1">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold bg-white/20 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">4</span>
          <span class="font-semibold">Presentacion</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm/6 text-white/80">Dashboard operativo + App del conductor (PWA) + App ciudadana</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-eco-green/10 p-5 sm:p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-1">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold bg-eco-green/10 text-eco-green px-2 py-0.5 rounded">3</span>
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">IA + Optimizacion</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm/6 text-gray-600">OR-Tools (TSP) + MLPRegressor (prediccion) + IBM Watsonx (lenguaje natural)</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-50/80 p-5 sm:p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-1">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold bg-eco-green/10 text-eco-green px-2 py-0.5 rounded">2</span>
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Procesamiento en la nube</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm/6 text-gray-600">FastAPI + PostgreSQL/PostGIS + IBM Cloud</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-50/40 p-5 sm:p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-1">
          <span class="text-xs font-bold bg-eco-green/10 text-eco-green px-2 py-0.5 rounded">1</span>
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Captura de datos</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm/6 text-gray-600">Sensores IoT (50 contenedores, 3 zonas) + Reportes ciudadanos (app movil) + Datos historicos</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Tech badges -->
  <div class="mx-auto mt-10 max-w-4xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2">
      {techStack.map(tech => (
        <span class="text-sm/6 text-gray-600 bg-gray-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full ring-1 ring-gray-900/10">{tech}</span>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
